By Cedric Pabriga,�Triforce,�Jen Rothery,�+27 more
updatedJun 27, 2024

This Genshin Impact Wiki guide details everything you need to know about�the Genshin Impact banner schedule for past, current, and next Genshin Impact banners, including the 4.7 Genshin Impact Banners and upcoming 4.7 Banners.

advertisement

A big part of Genshin Impact is the Wish system. Most of the game�s playable characters and best weapons are found here, with regularly refreshed �banners� introducing new characters and boosting the appearance rates of others.

As the world of Teyvat grows older, the list of banners past and present will continue to grow. Here�s a complete catalog of which banners have been and gone, all currently available banners, and the "rate up" characters you have an increased chance of pulling from each.

Wanderlust Invocation is a permanent banner and will thus not be included here. All non-limited characters and weapons are available through it at their standard rates.

advertisement

What Is the Current Genshin Impact Banner?

The current banners for Phase 2 of Version 4.7 features Sigewinne and Furina as the featured 5-Star characters, with Noelle, Gaming, and Rosaria as the 4-Stars.
